# compile_commands.json is generated by "pio run" and used by clangd.
# Excluding it means anyone who clones must build once before
# C IntelliSense fully works — document this in your README.
# Alternatively, commit it for instant clangd support on clone:
# (uncomment the next line to commit it)
# !.pio/build/tractor_esp32/compile_commands.json

# OS noise
